title: Dusty Baker: I once smoked a joint with Jimi Hendrix in San Francisco
text: Dusty Baker: I once smoked a joint with Jimi Hendrix in San Francisco Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (1 minute ago) Teenage Dusty Baker once shared some conversation and a little "grass" with Jimi Hendrix, according to a new account of how music shaped the life of the baseball great.
